%% stateful-agents — two-worker race (slide 12)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant A as Worker A
    participant R as Redis
    participant B as Worker B

    A->>R: GET agent:demo-001
    R-->>A: state @ step=FETCH_DATA, fetch_index=2
    B->>R: GET agent:demo-001
    R-->>B: state @ step=FETCH_DATA, fetch_index=2

    Note over A,B: both workers compute step 3 in parallel<br/>neither knows the other exists

    A->>R: SET agent:demo-001 (fetch_index=3, data=[…A])
    B->>R: SET agent:demo-001 (fetch_index=3, data=[…B])

    Note over R: silent corruption — last write wins.<br/>A's data section is gone forever.
